Text.string: That was a close one. / I nearly kicked the bucket, / which would really suck.
Thanks for the revive. / I really needed that one. / You're super awesome.
You and me, a team. / Real heroes are the ones that / save each other's hides.
Let's not dwell on this. / A momentary setback, / maybe I just tripped.
I was not worried. / They would not have killed me off / outside a cutscene.
Use this grenade. Or not. Your call.
Did you try dodging the bullets?
You can do it! Rise, Vault Hunter!
Hold these bullets in your face.
Can you see me? I can see you.
We are a unit. / Teamwork means a helping hand / can turn the battle.
You made a mistake / trying to headbutt bullets. / I have so been there.
I shall save your life. / You will owe me a favor. / Grab my dry cleaning.
No cause for alarm. / Dying is part of the plan. / Just make THEM do it.
Easy, Vault Hunter. / If you die now, we have no / NPCs next game.
What happened to you? / You should be better than this. / Alas, here we are.
Your hunt will not end. / I am here to revive you. / Meet Death sometime else.
Return to me, FL4K. / There is so much left to hunt. / I won't let you go.
Don't give them this kill. / They are not worthy of you. / We will make them pay.
Arise, Beastmaster. / Your pack is too strong to fall. / Get back on your feet.
On your feet, soldier. / This battle is not yet won. / I need you alive.
Get back in the fight. / I need a badass teammate, / and you fit the bill.
Moze. You're not a mech. / You cannot deflect bullets. / Did you get confused?
Time to get up, Moze. / I made breakfast with waffles. / Not really. I lied.
How did that happen? / I looked away and you were / on the ground, dying.
Zane, buddy. Come on. / We talked about this last time. / No battlefield naps.
That's a nice jacket. / Sorry, I got distracted / while reviving you.
Got taken down, huh? / Happens to the best of us. / It comes with the job.
Just like old times, Zane. / We were great contract killers. / Simpler days, I guess.
Are you okay, Zane? / You got a pain overdose / right in your old face.
Get up, Amara. / Don't give them even an inch. / You're better than them.
You must fight the pain. / It is insignificant / compared to your skill.
This is not your time. / There are so many douchebags / we still need to kill.
Not today, Siren. / Fight at my side once again. / Let's kick their asses.
If I had eight arms, / I would high-five a spider. / Just a thought I had.
